        "React",
        "Performance"
      ],
      "excerpt": "Learn how to optimize React applications for better performance.",
      "content": "<h1>React Performance Guide</h1><p>React applications can become slow if components re-render unnecessarily.</p><h2>Why Performance Matters</h2><p>Performance directly affects user experience.</p><h3>Common Issues</h3><ul><li>Unnecessary re-renders</li><li>Large component trees</li><li>Heavy computations</li></ul><h2>Optimization</h2><h3>React.memo</h3><pre><code>const MyComponent = React.memo((props)=>{ return &lt;div&gt;{props.title}&lt;/div&gt; })</code></pre><blockquote>Measure performance first before optimizing.</blockquote><p>Use profiling tools to detect bottlenecks.</p>",
