      "excerpt": "Best practices when designing scalable Node.js systems.",
      "content": "<h1>Node.js Architecture Tips</h1><p>Designing scalable systems requires clear architecture.</p><h2>Layered Architecture</h2><ul><li>Routes</li><li>Controllers</li><li>Services</li><li>Repositories</li></ul><h3>Benefits</h3><p>Separating logic makes the application easier to maintain.</p><pre><code>class UserService { static async findAll(){ return await User.findAll() }}</code></pre><blockquote>Good architecture improves scalability.</blockquote>",
