      ],
      "excerpt": "Redux Toolkit simplifies Redux development significantly.",
      "content": "<h1>Understanding Redux Toolkit</h1><p>Redux Toolkit simplifies state management in React apps.</p><h2>Main Features</h2><ul><li>createSlice</li><li>configureStore</li><li>createAsyncThunk</li></ul><h3>Example Slice</h3><pre><code>const slice = createSlice({ name:'counter', initialState:{value:0}, reducers:{increment:(state)=>{state.value++}}})</code></pre><blockquote>Redux Toolkit is the recommended way to write Redux.</blockquote>",
