      "excerpt": "Containerize your Node.js applications easily.",
      "content": "<h1>Deploy Node Apps with Docker</h1><p>Docker packages applications into containers.</p><h2>Benefits</h2><ul><li>Consistent environment</li><li>Easy deployment</li><li>Better scaling</li></ul><h3>Dockerfile Example</h3><pre><code>FROM node:20 WORKDIR /app COPY package.json . RUN npm install COPY . . CMD ['npm','start']</code></pre><blockquote>Containers eliminate environment inconsistencies.</blockquote>",
