      "excerpt": "Create scalable REST APIs using Express.js.",
      "content": "<h1>Building REST API with Express</h1><p>Express is a minimalist framework for Node.js.</p><h2>API Structure</h2><ul><li>Routes</li><li>Controllers</li><li>Services</li></ul><h3>Example Route</h3><pre><code>app.get('/users', async(req,res)=>{ const users=await User.findAll(); res.json(users) })</code></pre><blockquote>Separate business logic from routes.</blockquote>",
